Package thing.dna

Class C_GenePair

  • java.lang.Object
    • thing.dna.C_GenePair
  • public class C_GenePair
extends java.lang.Object
    A gene pair is a couple of gene on homologous chromosomes. One is on the chromosome from the mother, and the other on the chromosome from the father. Both are on the same position on the two chromosomes. This position is a "locus". However, their values of alleles are not necessarily the same.
    Author:
    kyle wagner, elyk@acm.org Version 1.0, Fri Dec 15 11:16:26 2000
